data.title: Netball Wellington Centre
data.meta_description: Netball for Wellingtonians: player, coach, umpire, technical official, manager, administrator, supporter & volunteer - any age, stage, gender & ability welcome!
data.text:
Please find below and attached in PDF a complete list of netball tournaments on offer throughout the Netball Central Zone and beyond for all age level groups in 2024.

Confirmed at 16 February 2024. Events shown in red italic to be confirmed (plotted based on 2023 timing).

Feel free to contact the Host Centre listed or visit their website for further information about entry to any of these events.

Following the introduction of the Year 7&8 Player Development Programme (PDP) in 2018, Year 7&8 representative tournaments are no longer endorsed by Netball NZ or Zones.
